snippet.title: Hidden Expedition 5 The Uncharted Islands Full Walkthrough Better Version No Commentary
snippet.description: Greetings Players and Adventures, Previously on Hidden Expedition, You were sent into the mysterious Bermuda Triangle to find an ace pilot agent of HEAT or Hidden Expedition Adventure Team went into the Bermuda Triangle, you uncovered that the victims that went in the Bermuda Triangle got trapped by the Da Vinci Node invented by Leonardo Da Vinci which was stolen by Gideon, the force field grant them eternal life, but it makes people trapped there by this one way door. So now the people of the Uncharted Islands ask for your help to stop Undertow and Save them before its to late. This walkthrough will help you continue your mission and to put an end to the Pirate Undertow. You will also find a bonus chapter that will help you get back to New York City and to transport what you got to the Hidden Expedition Vault. So good luck adventurers and Players!
